snippet.title: LongbowX - Failrace Staff
snippet.description: Hey, most people have seen me racing on FailRace's main channel, but this channel is where I post companion content: my own perspective on races, challenges and Survive the Hunt videos. With more behind-the-scenes content to come, including unseen Survive the Hunt episodes!
